NOVATEK MICROELE said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 8.44% to NT$2,805,739,000 from NT$3,064,380,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales           2,805,739        3,064,380   
YOY%              -8.44%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           10,313,916       11,443,623  
YOY%              -9.87% 
=================================================================
 